                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Taylor</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-02-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 5, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Queen approved. Will appear in Gazette to-morrow, when telegram will be sent
                    immediately to Cuba, putting it into effect.</p>
            </div>
